Description_lang: Fills a player with a Deathwish, causing them to walk towards the edge of the arena and jump off the platform to their death upon reaching it.When the player jumps, or when Deathwish is dispelled, Deathwish inflicts $275991s1 Shadow damage to all players. This damage is reduced by range. In addition, several Minions of Zul are created.
AuraDescription_lang: Forced to walk to your death.Inflicts damage reduced by range and creates Minions of Zul upon removal.
